Package: UZIMA
Title: UZIMA External Researcher Data Access
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Derick", "Imbati", email = "derick.imbati@aku.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Connection helpers and examples for accessing UZIMA Fabric data
    from Microsoft Fabric. Supports multiple authentication methods including
    Service Principal with Key Vault, device code flow, and environment variables.
